[src:chaos-engineering-tools/chaos-engineering-the-history-principles-and-practice] You can also watch speakers from Failover Conf, which is themed more around reliability and adapting to changing technology trends.
[src:chaos-engineering-tools/chaos-engineering-the-history-principles-and-practice] The Chaos Engineering community is a global community of engineers.
